&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Business Administration, Human Resources, or a related field or previous experience in business consulting, workforce development, or a similar role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understand

