&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Career Team is a leading workforce development organization on a mission to transform lives.&amp;nbsp; We blend cutting-edge technology with compassionate, high-touch services to drive real, measurable outcomes in the lives of job seekers across the country.&amp;nbsp; At Career Team, we’re solving today’s unemployment challenges with smart software, world-class trainers, dedicated case managers, dynamic job developers, and innovative partners. If you&#39;re passionate about making a difference and believe in the power of technology to transform lives, you’ll feel right at home here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TITLE: &lt;/strong&gt;Director of Workforce Transformation&lt;/p&gt;
